It doesn't matter if your White, Black, Purple or Pink. It doesn't matter if your a Jew, Muslim, Christian or Hindu. IF you do something, you did it. If not... not. If Monica went down on the Pres... it happened. If she's Jewish doesn't make it better or worse.<br><br>
Owen... &quot;The Fundamentalist Islamic's must be seen for the cancer they are, and removed,completely and totally.&quot;<br>
